## ğŸ§  **Memory Tip:**

> Think of `**SNiTCH BuBBy**` ğŸ”‘
> S = str, N = numeric, i = int, T = tuple, C = complex, H = float
> B = bool, u = set, B = bytes, y = bytearray, etc.

